Las Vegas!': Ever seeking ways to raise capital to finance more evil robots, Dr. Eggman takes a 'gamble' that the new Throndyke Casino - owned by Sonic's best friend Chris' parents - might provide the 'jackpot' he needs. Will Sonic, Tails and his friends be able to stop Eggman or will there be a new 'king' in town complete with his own deadly two armed bandit? You'll have to read this issue to see what happens because 'what happens in this issue stays in this issue!'

"What Happens Here Stays in Here" "Viva Las V-Egg-As!"

description: A special stand-alone issue featuring art by Frazer Irving (SEVEN SOLDIERS: KLARION THE WITCHBOY). Back from the depths of Hell (literally) and devastated by the soul-wrenching events that took place there, John Constantine recalls the first time he ever worked his own unique brand of conjuring, with an emphasis on "con."
name: The Gift

description: The penultimate chapter of the epic "One World, Under Gog" explodes here as the Justice Society of America goes to war with one another. Torn between Gog's desire to help the world and the moral cost it comes with, it's old guard vs. the new as the line that was drawn is crossed. But Gog does not like war...
name: One World, Under Gog Part VI: Saints and Sinners

description: MAD strikes fear into the hearts of the summer's superheroes with our full spoof of Iron Man and our heroic jabs at Hellboy, Hancock and the Hulk! We also poke fun at the Olympics, the MTV Movie Awards, high gas prices and summer camps. Want more? How about a 4-page spoof of Circuit City and our Apple-bashing comic strip, "Calvin and Jobs"? And let's not forget, Spy vs. Spy, What the Heck is the Difference?, the Fold-In, the MAD Strip Club and much more! Don't be a hero – go buy this issue right now!
name: We Cover This Summer's Super Heroes!

description: Wolverine is back in Chinatown, settling old scores. First up, his vengeful ex-girlfriend. Only problem, she now commands an army of gun-toting thugs, along with four mystical Kung Fu warriors, who together put a beatdown on Wolvie the likes of which hasn’t been seen in years. Now with Wolverine driven into hiding and the entire city out searching for him, who will dare come to his aid?
name: Part Two: Black Dragon Death Squad To The Edge Of Panic

description:
After seeing her father and mother (again!) die, Cassie Hack was stunned. Unable to help her, Vlad calls Georgia, one of Cassie's best friends. In the meantime in Indiana, Chris and Lisa receive a visit from Hell. A killer sent to take Pooch back to Hell and capture Cassie Hack for punishment.

Meanwhile, sad and alone, Vlad fought against some creatures that used to haunt Cassie's dreams but he couldn't talk this with Cassie who decided not only to quit her life as a slasher but to finally open up her heart and kiss Georgia.

Will Cassie and Vlad be able to have a normal life? What will happen with Lisa and Chris who are in the hands of this hellish creature? And what's the role of Ashley Guthrie in all this nightmare?
name: Closer, Part 1

description: Dara's path of revenge continues. After killing Zakros, the whole world were aware not only of her sudden resurrection but of Zakro's power as well. Nevertheless, the hunt for Knossos cannot be delayed. With the help of their friends, Dara found out her enemy in Mexico. But Knossos will prove why is he the most powerful of the 3 brothers.

Puzzles, puzzles everywhere---Solve them and win a one-way trip to Hell...

If crosswords are your game, we have one where the solutions lie deep within your very soul.

If you think you have the coordination, figure out the door that imprisons one of Hell's smallest emissaries.

And if you find Hell's not all you'd hoped, perhaps one of Morte Mamme's cadre - Ron Ringwood - can bring you home again.

No matter what happens, though, you're in for one Hell of a time...

  • Wordsworth
  • Girl in the Peephole
  • The Last Laugh
name: Wordsworth; Girl in the Peephole; The Last Laugh

description: In this issue we meet the members of the World Protection and Crisis Agency, striving to protect the remaining scientists of the World Peace Orginization before they are wiped out by the agents of Tengu. The W.P.C.A. has the manpower to stop the Tengu plot, but can they find out the plan in time?

The bold new era of Dungeons & Dragons continues with this brand-new series from acclaimed Nightwing penciller Mike Lilly and JLA writer Sean Smith! Aidus, a young paladin in command of an isolated border colony, soon realizes his inexperience is more than dangerous... it's deadly! Raiding orcs, a fiery sorceress, true love, and mysterious new companions are only a few of the dangers Aidus must face, as tensions in the border town bubble over!
name: Born Of Fire

description: The sequel to In the Shadow of Dragons! A forbidden romance between the children of two warring leaders sparks a tale of magic, betrayal, kidnapping, and rising undead. Death, romace, murder, and revenge,  it's all here!

name: Razor: Year One; Arizona: The Wild; Killing Machine; Sade

description: While the paladin Aidus journeys to the capital with his new ally, the powerful sorcerer Zed-Kraken, the beautiful half-elf Vail fights a lone battle against a pair of savage were-rats! Will Aidus survive a duel to the death, not to mention political conflicts and assassinations? And who are the mysterious were-rats, and what of the other pair watching and waiting in the shadows? And what is the tragic past that ties all our heroes together? Find out, if you dare!
name: Forged In Tears

description: The bold new era of Dungeons & Dragons continues! In the capital city, Aidus and Zed-Kraken continue to struggle against their mysterious and powerful attacker. Meanwhile, the rest of the fellowship bands together for a dangerous journey into the Barrier Peaks, hoping to bring an end to Mistress Flame's reign of destruction. Will anyone survive to reach the end of the story? And just who is the griffon-riding "Stealth"... a strange new ally, or a deadly new enemy? Find out, if you dare....
name: Tempered In Fellowship

description: The paladin Aidus and his adventurers confront the Minions of Evil within a forgotten dungeon. Traps, undead guardians and the Fire Sorceress Mistress Flame all wait to test the companions. Who will fall in battle? The fantastic conclusion to the Tempest Gate mini-series!
name: Sheathed In Justice

description: With the deaths of the hero, who can possible track down the army of bandits and goblins planning to crush the elves of Phostwoods? A tavern brawl, a furious horse race, a fortune teller, the return of an old friend, and more in this issue!

The heroes make their way to the entrance of Cerin's hideaway, but a fierce battle awaits them. Meanwhile, the smell of treachery keeps Abehhan-Vrre and his entourage very suspicious of one another. But animosities are suspended as they lay the perfect trap for our unsuspecting heroes.

The heroes try to escape from the forces of Abehhan-Vrre, but not without the loss of one of their own. And as the adventurers discover their time has unexpectedly run out, the Rise begins, and the undead converge upon the Phostwoods!

The nail-biting conclusion to this fast-paced story brings the heroes back to the Phostwoods where the undead are rising. As Abehhan-Vrre prepares his invasion, our adventurers return with Lumari in the nick of time. But will her father be able to make a heart-wrenching decision no leader should ever make? And will Kiernan be able to let the pieces fall where they may? Don't miss the incredible finale of this beautiful, pulse- pounding series!

Three short tales of death and murder. 
 
Poison short story 
Sade/Rose & Gunn 
Edens Wrath

Hellina discovers that the mayor of Chicago has joined a splinter group of the Seventh Day and is threatening to release an airborne virus which should kill the entire population of Chicago. Battling her way to the mayor, Hellina is joined by Nira-X. Nira-X is able to erase the virus from existence, while Hellina defeats the mayor.

Tira Jane is the elven princess of her tribe and when her captain, Baldric returns with news of the battle at theirs lands boarders and the treaties signed to ensure peace with their neighboring tribes, Tira is more interested in sex. 
 
She keeps her captain for herself all night and come morning her town has been laid siege to by man-beasts. With baldric incapacitated Tira charges naked from her home with sword in hand. She battles valiantly until she is knocked to the ground and loses her sword. Baldric come to her aid and they repel the invaders. 
 
meanwhile from a vantage point bald, more technological looking, elves watch the battle they set in place, with drugged water and aggravating the man-beasts against the town, failing and lament that they will have to return to their princess Shania with the news. 
 
Back in Atlantis the elves report tot heir princess who calmly makes the lead elf explode with the pointing of her finger and orders the remaining pair to go and see that Tira does not reach this city and that her sister must die!
name: The Savage Awakening!
Searching For Trust
Top Cat! (Or, "Pardon me, but your Gronk ate our Princess!)

description: Even in a world where magic is an accepted fact, and Satan uses advertising agencies to encourage people to commit sins and go to Hell, the suicidal Zane didn't expect that an actual personification of Death would walk through his door just before he pulled the trigger to shoot himself in the head. Startled, Zane accidentally shot Death, and killed him. In the aftermath of this, Zane discovers that abstract concepts such as Death, as well as Fate, Time, Love and so on, are all represented by human avatars who do the job for a time until circumstances force others to take up their role, and that by slaying the previous Death, Zane has inherited the title. Now Zane is responsible for collecting the souls of those about to die, and judging them to decide whether they go to Heaven, Hell or somewhere else.
